      </p>
      <div class="rifath-quote rifath-quote--mobile">
        <div class="side-border"></div>
        <p>"Eventhex.ai is a game changer in the event tech space. We had first-hand experience using their platform for the Youth Business Conclave. Personally, I was impressed by their UI/UX design capabilities. We highly recommend this team to anyone looking for an innovative event tech solution!"</p>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-author">
        <img src="https://cms.eventhex.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Group-2233.png" alt="SOLID Business Club logo" class="author-logo" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="https://cms.eventhex.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Rifath-Rahman.jpeg" alt="Rifath Rahman" class="author-avatar" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="author-info">
          <h4 class="author-name">Rifath Rahman</h4>
